*bttn-jelly
*bttn-gradient
*bttn-fill
*bttn-material-circle
*bttn-material-flat
*bttn-pill
*bttn-float
*bttn-unite
*bttn-slant (Beta)

;Button sizes

*bttn-xs
*bttn-sm
*bttn-md
*bttn-lg

;Button Colors

*bttn-default
*bttn-primary
*bttn-warning
*bttn-success
*bttn-danger
*bttn-royal

;Button helper classes

*bttn-block
*bttn-no-outline (Don't show outline when navigating with keyboard/interact using mouse or touch)






